---
title: Buttery-Sage Pork with Crushed Potatoes, Veggies and Toasted Pepitas
description: Two techniques in this recipe are absolute musts to add to any cook’s repertoire. The first is smashed potatoes, less work than mash, but soft and textured in just the right way. The second is butter basting a steak. The final result, an amazingly juicy and tender piece of meat, is well worth the effort.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b721bc330006c357b6a8d63-2e26d018.jpg
